name: NEON ANIMALS
description:
Future Vision Series

With pet ownership only available to a wealthy few - animated animal street lights populate dark city streets providing comfort and companionship to lonely city dwellers. 

Modelled on early internet cat and dog GIFs, the AI memory and gait recognition provides unintentional entertainment, with cats getting stuck in loops — playing with rain and running water.

1080x1080. 24fps. Featuring original score.
